      <h1>MOHRE Work Permit Documents</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">The Employee's Guide to Document Preparation</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Your employer handles the work permit application. Your job is to prepare the documents. This guide covers what you need, how to get it attested, and what causes rejections — from the employee's perspective.</p>

      <div class="service-snapshot">
        <div class="snapshot-item">
